original_title: Dorothy and Toto's Storytime: The Wonderful Wizard of Oz Part 3
overview: It's story time! Take a ride with Dorothy and her best pal Toto as they share their favorite adventures in the magical land of Oz. Enter a legendary world in this storybook rendition of L. Frank Baum's beloved classic tale, Dorothy And Toto's Storytime: The Wonderful Wizard Of Oz Part 3!
title: Dorothy and Toto's Storytime: The Wonderful Wizard of Oz Part 3
